# 🎯 SkillQuest – Career Discovery

A beginner-friendly Career Discovery System built using **Python**, **HTML**, and **CSS**. This project recommends a suitable technology career based on the user's interests, favorite subject, strengths, and skill level. It also provides a personalized learning roadmap, required skills, achievement badges, motivational quotes, and an attractive HTML report.

