# 📝 Project Description

SkillQuest is a beginner-friendly career guidance application developed using Python fundamentals.

The program recommends a suitable technology career according to the user's interests, favorite subject, strengths, and skill level. It also provides the required skills, a learning roadmap, achievement badges, progress level, motivational quotes, and a beautiful HTML-based career report to guide students toward their future career.

