# ▶️ How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository.
2. Open the project in **Google Colab** or any Python IDE.
3. Run the Python program.
4. Enter your name.
5. Select your area of interest.
6. Enter your favorite subject.
7. Enter your biggest strength.
8. Choose your skill level.
9. View your personalized career report.

